{"tid":469530,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[召集連登既修真者] 論修仙悟道的可能性","createTime":"2017-11-15T11:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T05:25:34.000Z","uid":75100,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ceaa4ddcc5716882c1a20b9a29e675832429fd53","tid":469530,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:45:47.000Z","msg":"相信有人都睇過修仙小說，而網上也確確實實有好多修真方面既秘籍，可以係鍊體法 , 內功功法，或者林林總總既茅山法術/風水算命。<br />\n<br />\n我手上有幾本普通既功法，佢話可以幫我打通到大周天，但我資質差，連功法入面既好多動作都未跟得哂，更加唔好講感覺到氣感<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知好玄幻， 唔講用御空取物，或者去到結金丹同埋元嬰期呢D咁勁，但我覺得現實黎講，應該到達煉氣期 , 甚至築基期應該都有可能吧? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da7d663a802f59e2e850d325193fab86d133acf","tid":469530,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇圖？"},{"pid":"29efb810fdffefb54a22947c1846728ce3eb6427","tid":469530,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:56:17.000Z","msg":"簡體字見諒，畢竟係大陸傳出黎既功法。<br />\n<br />\n我既理解，大概就係先用吐納法，存左一定份量既氣係丹田，然後就用個股氣黎衝脈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/195359_29a638fae7ff31a6115d1102bfa4e685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F195359_29a638fae7ff31a6115d1102bfa4e685.jpg&h=d6fbc857&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86320e4cdea2353d21ceea593655315f2fc6e951","tid":469530,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:58:32.000Z","msg":"雖然知道連登應該唔會有真正既修真者，但有無曾經試過修道既巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c13d59a26d495126187d76d00a3b4babb9ae9a5","tid":469530,"uid":93266,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:59:04.000Z","msg":"現代既功法同心法 , 全部都係垃圾<br /